    {
      "id": "shushan_foot",
      "name": "蜀山脚下",
      "chapter": "序章",
      "description": "玩家进入蜀山世界的起点，山脚下的小村庄",
      "recommended_level": [1, 5],
      "script": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "type": "cutscene",
          "content": "山路蜿蜒，远处仙山隐约可见云雾之中。山脚下，几户人家炊烟袅袅。",
          "narration": "你沿山路而来，眼前便是传说中的蜀山。仙气缭绕，好一派仙家气象。"
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "guide_npc",
          "text": "年轻人，你也是来蜀山求道的？我叫老王，在这山脚做了几十年引路人。"
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "type": "tutorial",
          "tutorial_type": "movement",
          "content": "学习移动操作：WASD移动，空格跳跃，鼠标控制视角"
        },
        {
          "step": 4,
          "type": "explore",
          "area": "shushan_foot_village",
          "objectives": ["与铁匠老张对话", "与药铺掌柜对话", "探索村庄"],
          "npcs": ["blacksmith_zhang", "medicine_shop_owner"]
        },
        {
          "step": 5,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "guide_npc",
          "text": "山上最近有妖狼作祟，你若要上山，需先有些自保之力。不如去山脚猎几只狼练练手？"
        },
        {
          "step": 6,
          "type": "tutorial",
          "tutorial_type": "combat",
          "content": "学习基础战斗：左键攻击，右键防御，1234使用技能，Q喝药"
        },
        {
          "step": 7,
          "type": "battle",
          "enemies": ["wolf"],
          "count": 3,
          "is_tutorial": true,
          "location": "shushan_foot_forest"
        },
        {
          "step": 8,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "guide_npc",
          "text": "不错！你有修行的天资。随我来，我引你上山。"
        },
        {
          "step": 9,
          "type": "explore",
          "area": "shushan_foot",
          "objectives": ["收集狼牙 x5", "采集灵草 x3", "探索山脚全境"],
          "enemies": ["wolf", "boar", "wild_dog"]
        },
        {
          "step": 10,
          "type": "quest",
          "quest_id": "sq_001",
          "giver": "blacksmith_zhang",
          "auto_trigger": false
        },
        {
          "step": 11,
          "type": "quest",
          "quest_id": "sq_002",
          "giver": "medicine_shop_owner",
          "auto_trigger": false
        },
        {
          "step": 12,
          "type": "boss_battle",
          "boss": "wolf_king",
          "location": "wolf_den",
          "trigger": "进入狼王洞穴",
          "cutscene_before": {
            "content": "洞穴深处传来低沉的咆哮，一双幽绿的眼睛在黑暗中闪烁。",
            "narration": "你握紧手中的剑，缓缓走入洞穴..."
          }
        },
        {
          "step": 13,
          "type": "cutscene",
          "content": "狼王倒下，洞穴深处隐隐发光...",
          "narration": "你在洞穴中发现了一把古朴的铁剑，剑身隐隐有灵光流转。"
        },
        {
          "step": 14,
          "type": "item_get",
          "item": "iron_sword",
          "description": "获得铁剑 - 剑身古朴，但隐隐有灵气流转"
        },
        {
          "step": 15,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "guide_npc",
          "text": "看来你已有些本事了。走吧，去凝碧崖，峨眉派就在那里。"
        },
        {
          "step": 16,
          "type": "transition",
          "target_level": "ningbi_cliff",
          "method": "fast_travel"
        }
      ],
      "enemies": [
