    {
      "id": "ningbi_cliff",
      "name": "峨眉凝碧崖",
      "chapter": "第一卷",
      "description": "峨眉派所在地，修仙者云集的圣地",
      "recommended_level": [5, 15],
      "script": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "type": "cutscene",
          "content": "凝碧崖上，云雾缭绕，仙鹤翩飞。远处山峰耸立，道观隐现。",
          "narration": "你终于来到了传说中的峨眉派，正道领袖的所在。"
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "zhuge_jingwo",
          "text": "你是来拜师的？我是诸葛警我，峨眉派大师兄。随我来，我带你去见掌门。"
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "type": "escort",
          "target": "zhuge_jingwo",
          "destination": "main_hall"
        },
        {
          "step": 4,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "miaoyi_zhenren",
          "text": "你是新入门的弟子？好。峨眉门规森严，当恪守正道，勤勉修行。"
        },
        {
          "step": 5,
          "type": "ceremony",
          "ceremony_type": "initiation",
          "description": "参加入门仪式，正式成为峨眉弟子"
        },
        {
          "step": 6,
          "type": "item_get",
          "item": "emei_disciple_robe",
          "description": "获得峨眉弟子袍 - 正式成为峨眉派弟子"
        },
        {
          "step": 7,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "li_yingqiong",
          "text": "你便是新来的弟子？我乃峨眉李英琼，这把紫郢剑便是我本命飞剑。"
        },
        {
          "step": 8,
          "type": "quest",
          "quest_id": "mq_004",
          "giver": "li_yingqiong",
          "auto_trigger": true
        },
        {
          "step": 9,
          "type": "tutorial",
          "tutorial_type": "cultivation",
          "content": "学习修炼系统：打坐修炼、提升境界、学习技能"
        },
        {
          "step": 10,
          "type": "explore",
          "area": "ningbi_cliff",
          "objectives": ["拜访各长老", "学习基础功法", "探索凝碧崖"],
          "npcs": ["miaoyi_zhenren", "zhuge_jingwo", "li_yingqiong", "zhou_qingyun", "qi_lingyun"]
        },
        {
          "step": 11,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "changmei_zhenren",
          "text": "（影像）来者何人？...原来是新入门的弟子。吾乃长眉，虽已飞升，但留影像于凝碧崖，指点后辈。"
        },
        {
          "step": 12,
          "type": "skill_learn",
          "skill": "basic_qi_cultivation",
          "teacher": "changmei_zhenren",
          "description": "学习基础吐纳术"
        },
        {
          "step": 13,
          "type": "quest",
          "quest_id": "sq_006",
          "giver": "zhi_xian",
          "auto_trigger": false,
          "trigger_location": "garden_area"
        },
        {
          "step": 14,
          "type": "battle",
          "enemies": ["demon_scout"],
          "count": 3,
          "trigger": "夜晚时分",
          "cutscene_before": {
            "content": "夜深人静，几个黑影潜入凝碧崖...",
            "narration": "你发现了可疑的入侵者！"
          }
        },
        {
          "step": 15,
          "type": "cutscene",
          "content": "入侵者被击退，但留下了五台派的信物...",
          "narration": "看来五台派蠢蠢欲动，正邪之争即将开始。"
        },
        {
          "step": 16,
          "type": "quest",
          "quest_id": "mq_008",
          "giver": "miaoyi_zhenren",
          "auto_trigger": true,
          "condition": "complete mq_004"
        }
      ],
      "enemies": [
