    {
      "id": "ciyun_temple",
      "name": "慈云寺",
      "chapter": "第一卷",
      "description": "五台派据点，正邪初次大规模冲突之地",
      "recommended_level": [15, 25],
      "script": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "type": "cutscene",
          "content": "慈云寺坐落在山谷之中，阴气森森。寺庙破败，但暗藏杀机。",
          "narration": "你来到慈云寺外围，五台派的据点就在眼前。"
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "zhu_mei",
          "text": "你就是峨眉派派来的？我是矮叟朱梅，青城派。我们联手围攻此寺！"
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "type": "battle",
          "enemies": ["wutai_disciple"],
          "count": 5,
          "location": "temple_entrance",
          "cutscene_before": {
            "content": "几个五台派弟子拦在门口，手持阴魂剑。",
            "narration": "五台派弟子阴笑着看向你..."
          }
        },
        {
          "step": 4,
          "type": "explore",
          "area": "ciyun_temple_outer",
          "objectives": ["清除外围敌人", "寻找入口机关", "收集情报"],
          "enemies": ["wutai_disciple", "demon_servant"]
        },
        {
          "step": 5,
          "type": "puzzle",
          "puzzle_type": "mechanism",
          "description": "破解寺门机关",
          "solution": "按照阴符排列顺序按下开关"
        },
        {
          "step": 6,
          "type": "cutscene",
          "content": "寺门缓缓打开，殿内传来阵阵阴气...",
          "narration": "你踏入慈云寺内部，黑暗中似乎有无数眼睛在注视着你。"
        },
        {
          "step": 7,
          "type": "battle",
          "enemies": ["wutai_disciple"],
          "count": 10,
          "location": "main_hall",
          "formation": "ambush"
        },
        {
          "step": 8,
          "type": "boss_battle",
          "boss": "xu_feiniang",
          "location": "inner_hall",
          "cutscene_before": {
            "content": "万妙仙姑许飞娘冷笑着走出，手中天魔诛仙剑散发着诡异的光芒。",
            "narration": "正邪对决，一触即发！"
          }
        },
        {
          "step": 9,
          "type": "cutscene",
          "content": "许飞娘身受重伤，却阴笑着退走...",
          "narration": "\"峨眉！这笔账我们五台派记下了！\""
        },
        {
          "step": 10,
          "type": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "zhu_mei",
          "text": "干得好！不过这只是开始，五台派不会善罢甘休。"
        },
        {
          "step": 11,
          "type": "boss_battle",
          "boss": "jile_daoren",
          "location": "secret_chamber",
          "trigger": "进入密室",
          "cutscene_before": {
            "content": "密室中，一个全身裹着绿袍的身影端坐...",
            "narration": "绿袍老祖！他竟在这里！"
          }
        },
        {
          "step": 12,
          "type": "cutscene",
          "content": "极乐道人突然出现，一道金光将绿袍老祖斩做两截！",
          "narration": "绿袍老祖惨叫一声，化为一道绿光遁走..."
        },
        {
          "step": 13,
          "type": "quest_completed",
          "quest_id": "mq_009"
        },
        {
          "step": 14,
          "type": "transition",
          "target_level": "ningbi_cliff",
          "method": "fast_travel"
        }
      ],
